text: "With Me" is a 2001 song by American country band Lonestar and is the second single from their fourth studio album I'm Already There. It went to number 63 in the United States and number 10 on the Billboard Hot Country Songs chart. ==References== Category:2001 songs Category:Country pop songs Category:Pop rock songs Category:Lonestar songs
title: With Me (Lonestar song)
